{"tid":1290121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"數十名天主教徒海富中心對出祈禱要求回應反修例訴求","createTime":"2019-07-06T11:20:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T11:29:04.000Z","uid":41404,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1c1c3c4114195f15353114d56321d1f5cc2b7e0d","tid":1290121,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T11:20:07.000Z","msg":"數十名天主教徒在金鐘海富中心對出參與祈禱會，要求政府回應反修例市民的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n他們唱聖詩、默哀及祈禱，又手持十字架步行至特首辦外。有教徒表示，行政長官林鄭月娥作為天主教徒，不單沒有尋找耶穌，還欺壓弱者，希望林鄭月娥認清身份，不要讓年輕人生活於驚恐當中。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有幾名市民在海富中心對出搭起帳篷絕食。參與絕食逾50小時的梁先生說，見到不少年輕人不滿政府處理修訂《逃犯條例》的手法，作為成年人以絕食明志，希望政府能安撫年輕人。他說，現時共有6位人士參與絕食，會堅持直至醫生認為他們不適宜繼續，才會停止絕食。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466958-20190706.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466958-20190706.htm&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zQjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=59a007d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466958-20190706.htm&h=a182ad67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466958-20190706.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f7ccd45b9f8c1358a443c8b30bf3c5a9bbd699f6","tid":1290121,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T11:21:38.000Z","msg":"各有各做<br />\n維持make noise"},{"pid":"28e58619c61199b4be722518a0e03bbfeb482273","tid":1290121,"uid":221696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T11:29:04.000Z","msg":"有無人印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<blockquote> <blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ykF0iKu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FykF0iKu.png&h=e791e1a6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F4VWBwa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF4VWBwa.png&h=c69769d7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LBEXk4h.